Catalogue
of the Lepidoptera of Belgium
Drepanidae
Geometridae
Thaumetopoeidae

The Geometridae are one of the largest families in the Lepidoptera with about 20000 described species. The family is distributed worldwide (Scoble 1992: 290).
Identification: Bleszynski 1965b, 1966, Forster & Wohlfahrt 1981, Hausmann 2001, Hoffmeyer 1966, Koch 1976, Mironov 2003, Prout 1912-1915, 1934-1939, Skinner 1984, Skou 1984, South 1972, Vojnits 1980, Wehrli 1939-1954.
Nomenclature according to Fauna Europaea.
Species in Belgium: 337.
